{"tid":1890892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣手足開左TG Channel","createTime":"2020-02-21T12:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T14:25:44.000Z","uid":152313,"like":106,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"8b286e493b5180d9c01bc1bcaed35811afc010ce","tid":1890892,"uid":152313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"巜願與流亡手足同開香檳》<br />\n<br />\n大家今晚咁高興攜同小鳳姐載歌載舞的同時，請大家不要忘記一班流亡海外的手足。<br />\n<br />\n今天的熱烈彈琴和掌聲，來自過去八個月的激烈的抗爭和槍聲。一個黑警確診肺炎，並不足以抵償手足們犧牲！<br />\n<br />\n從六月開始抗爭、身心流血受傷、家人離棄、付上前途、最終被逼永別自己成長的地方、帶着恐懼獨自面對未知的未來。<br />\n<br />\n這一群為我們付出一生的真手足，比起一個未死的肺炎武警，更加值得我哋關注。 請大家保持心的熱度，代流亡手足抗爭到底，直至光復的一天，與手足一同慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n@hkprotester_homeless<br />\n<br />\n#願有一天與你們在同一土地上共飲香檳<br />\n#齊上齊落<br />\n#同喜同悲<br />\n<br />\n#Cr. 黃姐姐代筆"},{"pid":"71115dfac7f232316968bb97d1eec542f0932680","tid":1890892,"uid":137506,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"g持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb82698c20583afc15e1391e567a9f5c6f8ff67b","tid":1890892,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bf3ec4cddb6a7da03197f3e124585344f36a6d","tid":1890892,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f065eea16d5d442a78f32a4fdf62549d8b3bfb","tid":1890892,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k